<sect1 id="container_page_1container_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <ref refid="classcontainer" kindref="compound">container</ref> class manages collections of events, graphs, and selections associated with a single input file or sample.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="container_page_1container_structure">
<title>Structure</title>
<para>Each container holds:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Metadata</bold>: Sample information (cross-section, etc.)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Events</bold>: Processed <ref refid="classevent__template" kindref="compound">event_template</ref> instances</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Graphs</bold>: Constructed <ref refid="classgraph__template" kindref="compound">graph_template</ref> instances</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Selections</bold>: Applied <ref refid="classselection__template" kindref="compound">selection_template</ref> results</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="container_page_1container_entry">
<title>Entry Structure</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="structentry__t" kindref="compound">entry_t</ref></computeroutput> structure groups related objects:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structentry__t" kindref="compound">entry_t</ref><sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::string<sp/><ref refid="structentry__t_1a18b538911b3605d930eae31cc72487cb" kindref="member">hash</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Event<sp/>hash</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::vector&lt;graph_t*&gt;<sp/><ref refid="structentry__t_1a45608e1c64eb289c8a31038f2542bfa1" kindref="member">m_data</ref>;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Graph<sp/>data</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
